# @COMMENT: The event is not found in HSNX. Turbān is only mentioned in HSNX as a loaction the submitters passed on their way to Badr (see HSNXV01P613B). A similar passage, that describes a delay caused by ʿĀʾishah that forced the people to perform tayammum is also found in WSACD and WSFAB. According to YNQXV04P004A, this refers to the same event where accusations were made against ʿĀʾishah after the raid on al-Muṣṭaliq (see HSNXV02P297A).

